
List DVB tuner devices

Usage: tslsdvb [options]

Options:

  -a N
  --adapter N
      This option can be used instead of device name.

  --debug[=level]
      Produce debug traces. The default level is 1. Higher levels produce more
      messages.

  -d name
  --device-name name
      By default, the first DVB receiver device is used. Use the tslsdvb
      utility to list all DVB devices.

  --help
      Display this help text.

  -v
  --verbose
      Produce verbose output.

  --version
      Display the TSDuck version number.

